0.1.name: wordpress/bns-support
0.1.description: Simple display of useful support information in the sidebar. Easy to copy and paste details, such as: the blog name; WordPress version; name of installed theme; and, active plugins list. Help for those that help. The information is only viewable by logged-in readers; and, by optional default, the blog administrator(s) only.
